# Optional. Copy to `.env.test` (or export in your shell) only if you want the Playwright suite
# to run against an already-deployed URL instead of building + previewing the app locally.
# Leave unset for normal local/CI runs — playwright.config.ts falls back to
# http://localhost:4173 (the local `vite preview` server it starts automatically) when this is
# not set, and skips starting that server entirely when it IS set.
#
# PLAYWRIGHT_BASE_URL=https://staging.example.com
